  <constraints>
    <constraint source="CLAUDE.md §3">**main-session-only** — sub-agents CANNOT write to `.claude/` paths. The task-execute skill MUST route this task to the main session.</constraint>
    <constraint source="CLAUDE.md §17">ADR authoring conventions — concise constraint version in `.claude/adr/` (≤80 lines, MUST/MUST NOT only); full version in `docs/adr/` (rationale, alternatives considered, consequences).</constraint>
    <constraint source="project">ADR number is dynamic — implementer determines via `Glob '.claude/adr/ADR-*.md'` at execution time; pick the next ordinal. DO NOT hardcode.</constraint>
